      <h1 class='title'>Scottish Executive Secondees</h1>
    </div>
    <div class='commons-written-statements-sitting' id='content'>
      
      <cite class='section'>HC Deb 16 September 2004 vol 424 c1689WS</cite>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_1689ws' title='Col. 1689WS &mdash; HC Deb 16 September 2004 vol 424 c1689WS' name='column_1689ws' href='#column_1689ws' rel='bookmark'>1689WS</a>
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_236'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-peter-duncan' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_236' title='Link to this speech by Mr Peter Duncan' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-peter-duncan" title="Mr Peter Duncan">Mr. Peter Duncan</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para">To ask the Secretary of State for Scotland how many staff in his Department are on secondment from the Scottish Executive. [187936]</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_237'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mrs-anne-mcguire' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_237' title='Link to this speech by Mrs Anne McGuire' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mrs-anne-mcguire" title="Mrs Anne McGuire">Mrs. McGuire</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para">There are presently 56 staff on loan to the Scotland Office from the Scottish Executive. In addition, 26 staff are on loan from the Scottish Executive to the Office of the Advocate-General for Scotland.</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
